<milestone unit="sentence" n="151" /> Prayer by <persName n="Jeter,Reverend,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00059" reg="mostcommon:Jeter,nomatch:0" authname="jeter"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev. Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Jeter</surname></persName>, of the <orgName n="Baptist Church" type="church">Baptist Church</orgName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="152" /> <persName n="Brown,Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00060" reg="mostcommon:Brown,nomatch:0" authname="brown"><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Brown</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Mississippi" key="tgn,7007522" authname="tgn,7007522">Mississippi</placeName>, offered a resolution tendering to <persName n="Buchanan,Admiral,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00061" reg="mostcommon:Buchanan,nomatch:0" authname="buchanan"><roleName n="Admiral" full="yes">Admiral</roleName> <surname full="yes">Buchanan</surname></persName> a privileged seat in the <name>Senate</name> during his stay in the city.

