<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="168" /> The Senate was called to order at <time value="11oclock">11 o'clock</time>. Prayer by <persName n="Converse,Reverend,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00068" reg="mostcommon:Converse,nomatch:0" authname="converse"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev. Dr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Converse</surname></persName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="169" /> In a very few minutes after being organized, and before any business, other than the reception and reference of a few resolutions and petitions, the <name>Senate</name> went into secret session. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="entry" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
