<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="170" /> The <rs type="place">House</rs> met at <time value="11am">11 A. M.</time>; and, after the transaction of some unimportant business, went into secret session.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="171" />When the doors were re-opened the <rs type="place">House</rs> adjourned. </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
<div2 type="later from the north" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
