<head><rs type="role2">Commissioner</rs>'s sale of <num value="2">two</num> negroes.</head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="424" /> --In pursuance of a decree of the <orgName n="Circuit Court" type="court">Circuit Court</orgName> of the city of <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 5" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName> as special <rs type="role2">Commissioner</rs> appointed therein.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="425" />I will proceed to sell, on <dateStruct value="--27" full="yes" authname="---27"><day type="name" full="yes">Monday</day>, <day reg="27" full="yes">27th instant</day></dateStruct>, at <time value="10oclock">10 o'clock</time> , at the auction-house of <persName n="Lee,,N.,M.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00271" reg="default:Lee,N.,M.,," authname="lee,n.,m."><foreName full="yes">N.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">M.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Lee</surname></persName>, <num value="1">one</num> Woman, named <persName n="Polly,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00272" reg="mostcommon:Polly,nomatch:0" authname="polly"><surname full="yes">Polly</surname></persName>, about <measure n="40years" type="date">forty years</measure> of age, who is a <num value="1">No. 1</num> cook, washer and ironer; also, a Boy, about <measure n="16years" type="date">sixteen years</measure> old, black and likely. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Jamfs,,R.,D.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00273" reg="default:Jamfs,R.,D.,," authname="jamfs,r.,d."><foreName full="yes">R.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">D.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Jamfs</surname></persName>, Executor and <rs type="role2">Commissioner</rs>.</signed> <term type="printrun">fe 24--tds</term> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
