<head><hi rend="smallcaps"><orgName n="Navy Department" type="department">Navy Department</orgName>,</hi><lb /><hi rend="smallcaps">Office special service.</hi><lb /><hi rend="smallcaps"><placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Va.</placeName>,</hi><dateStruct value="1864-09-19" full="yes" authname="1864-09-19"><month reg="09" full="yes">September</month> <day reg="19" full="yes">19</day>, <year reg="1864" full="yes">1864</year></dateStruct></head> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="444" />Notice.--From and after Monday Next, the <dateStruct value="--26" full="yes" authname="---26"><day reg="26" full="yes">26th instant</day></dateStruct>, the <term type="ship">Steamer</term> <rs type="ship">Shrapnel</rs> will leave the wharf at <placeName key="tgn,2625188" n="1.000 10" reg="Rocketts, Henrico, Virginia" authname="tgn,2625188">Rocketts</placeName> for the <orgName n="James River Squadron" type="squadron">James River Squadron</orgName> daily at <time value="7am">7 o'clock A. M.</time> and <time value="3pm">3 o'clock P. M.</time>, touching at all the principal landings on the river. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Parker,,John,H.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00281" reg="expanded:Parker," authname="parker"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">H.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Parker</surname></persName>.</signed> <lb /> <signed><rs type="role2">Lieutenant</rs> in charge.</signed> <term type="printrun">oc 20--ts</term> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
